data.description: MADE TO ENTERTAIN! This 3 BR, 2 BA Grain Valley home with it's open floor plan & sun room with bar is set up for fun! 11 x 17 newly stained deck & 11 x 11 gazebo with firepit & electric awaits your backyard parties. Flooring 4-5 yrs old & roof 5 yrs. 2 sheds with electric, 12 x 14 & 7 x 8 plus a wood shed. Vinyl siding, thermal windows. Two unfinished basement areas could add to your square footage or make great storage. Priced at $250,000.
